# Title: Potential AVKkid.DLL Sideloading
# Author: X__Junior (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2023-08-03
# Level: medium
# Description: Detects potential DLL sideloading of "AVKkid.dll"
# MITRE Tactic: Persistence
# Tags: attack.persistence, attack.privilege-escalation, attack.execution, attack.stealth, attack.t1574.001
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/image_load/image_load_side_load_avkkid.yml

ImageLoaded="*\\AVKkid.dll" NOT (ImageLoaded IN ("C:\\Program Files (x86)\\G DATA\\*", "C:\\Program Files\\G DATA\\*") Image IN ("*C:\\Program Files (x86)\\G DATA\\*", "*C:\\Program Files\\G DATA\\*") Image="*\\AVKKid.exe")